## ðŸ›ï¸ Overview
The **Mythosblock Drip Gateway** is the primary visualization and coordination layer for the Eternum network. It serves as a high-speed interface for monitoring testnet traffic and managing faucet distribution across the "Shadow Node" infrastructure.

## ðŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
- **Framework:** [Next.js 14](https://nextjs.org/) (App Router)
- **Visualization:** [Chart.js](https://www.chartjs.org/) via `react-chartjs-2`
- **Deployment:** [Vercel Edge Network](https://vercel.com/)
- **Email:** [Zoho Mail](https://zoho.com/mail) (Secure Identity: kitsune@mythosblock.com)

## ðŸ“Š Dashboard Components
- **Live Testnet Traffic:** Real-time distribution visualization of faucet requests.
- **Identity Layer:** Professional mail-exchange (MX) routing via Zoho.
- **Data Source:** `public/drip-stats.json` (Automated JSON pipe).

